{
  "stem": "25381.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He didn't want to go no place, nowhere-- very stubborn, stubborn like a rock.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Didn't want to listen-- he doesn't want to go no place except in New York.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He wants to stay in New York.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had no choice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I couldn't fight him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He didn't give in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My husband, I'm talking about.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After six weeks, I said to him, you know what?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I find out that every city from Europe-- like Berezne, [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH], you know, one next to the other-- has organization here.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they belong to-- and has a society.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they belong to the society.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You watch the baby-- I'm the one that's going to be brave.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm going to go to the office from the HIAS, and I'll talk to them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said, OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I went down to the office, and I was brave, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was-- how old was I? 22 years old, when I came to United States.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was married.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was 19.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I came to the office and I say, who is the-- the director from the office?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I come from this and this city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I say, I would like to find out-- my father is from this and this city-- I was born in Berezne.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was a [NON-ENGLISH], a different city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And maybe there's-- if they have a [NON-ENGLISH] society, a group.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I'm going to go there, and I would like to find out their meeting, and I'm going to say that I'm this and this daughter.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And maybe they'll find us a job or something-- an apartment, because we've been here, already, for six weeks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And in Hebrew they say, [NON-ENGLISH], how long we're going to stay in this HIAS building, and stay in the line for some food.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
